snippet.title: LIMINAL PHASE Gameplay Trailer (PCVR) - HD
snippet.description:
#vrgaming #vrhorror #indiegame
The second trailer for our VR action horror game called LIMINAL PHASE.
Wishlist on Steam 👉 https://store.steampowered.com/app/1999630/LIMINAL_PHASE/

About the game
LIMINAL PHASE is a VR action horror game set in an alternate '90s. Fight disturbing monsters, solve peculiar puzzles, and explore a fractured mind that is obsessed with videogames.

Featured in the Upload VR Showcase Summer 2022
https://youtu.be/8TDD5vZ8F_0

By AlcA Studio: https://alcastudio.com/welcome
